snippet: A woman charged along with her newlywed husband with killing a man she met through Craigslist tells a newspaper that two other men had responded to her ad for companionship but never showed up....

headline.print_headline: Pa. Craigslist Killing Suspect Says 2 Never Showed
headline.main: Pa. Craigslist Killing Suspect Says 2 Never Showed

lead_paragraph: A woman charged along with her newlywed husband with killing a man she met through Craigslist tells a newspaper that two other men had responded to her ad for companionship but never showed up.
